Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agape-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agape...!\NGiven the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps our best course of action is to draw up an\Nofficial set of terms concerning Peter Grill's seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must approach this situation \Nin an efficient manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A TREATY REGARDING THE ALLOCATION OF\NPETER GRILL'S REPRODUCTIVE RESOURCES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are they about to strike \Na deal over my crotch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back against the wall... I \Nmean, how could I resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This wasn't supposed to \Nhappen," I keep denying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just disappear... \NI can't stand myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moping around, spouting lies, \Ngrieving a broken heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold on desperately to these \Nfeelings and shut my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does this stupid \Nguilt refuse to go away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suffocate under its weight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always discouraged by my weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drop to my knees and grovel at your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clinging selfishly to \Nthe hope for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of regret and powerless to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel my heart being torn apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on this night of endless shame and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I get my act together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got nothing but this pathetic self of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'S-Scuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone hear me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using magic oughtta be banned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That impact play of yours \Nis what ought to be banned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stimulates the flow \Nof Senpai's slam chowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:20.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8: Peter Grill and the Secret Treaty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...\NIt stimulates the flow of Senpai's slam chowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stimulates the flow \Nof Senpai's slam chowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies...?\NIt stimulates the flow of Senpai's slam chowder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my magic can control \Nthe way he shoots his goo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...?!\NWell, my magic can control the way he shoots his goo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my magic can control \Nthe way he shoots his goo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to point out a major \Nissue with this schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's biased in your favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How observant of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you're more than just a pair\Nof walking boobs, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike that wimpy, long-eared \Nfreak over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling "wimpy"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's reassess the agreement and create\Na final draft once we've reached a consensus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.\NUm, what about me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.\NUm, what about me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!\NUm, what about me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I get a say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I invisible or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a damn break, would you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The terms introduced by a unilateral\Ninterspecies treaty were enforced thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with the treaty, \NPeter Grill carried out his usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rigorous duties on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the first day of rest following the\Ntreaty's enactment had finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a good mood, \Ngettin' all decked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, I'm glad you asked, Tim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a rest day, as \Nestablished by the treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to revel in my freedom and spend\Nsome quality time with Luvellia-senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long-overdue date... Have fun, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you weren't waiting for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look even more beautiful than usual.\NI couldn't help but stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the old saying goes, "Flattery \Nwill get you nowhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with Luvellia-senpai, \NI feel at peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food here is exquisite, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you like it, \Nthat's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the guys down at the\NGuild rave about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for dragging you along\Non my shopping trip, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a great time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May it be bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have a scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shameful of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carelessly leaving a mark on the world's\Nstrongest warrior like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scar is a badge of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the reason why I get to spend this type\Nof quality time with my beloved senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you used to despise \Nme back then, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me like that, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish this moment would last forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you over there, Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coinkydink!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is she doing here...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on a date, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's a rest day, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck are you talkin' about, Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the perfect time to get \Na jump on those other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I get to hog your \Nhog all to myself, y'know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the whole point of a contract\Nto obey the damn thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait... Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and this young Ogre seem to have become\Nquite close friends lately, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked for my help with combat training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a real hands-on process...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kiddin', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only hand involved in that process\Nis mine wrapped around your
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're comin' with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us for a \Nmoment, Luvellia-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This date is a big deal. \NDon't blow it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how's about we start off with a quickie?\NThat'll keep me happy for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "start off with" \Nlike it's an appetizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she keeps hanging around,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the short time I have left with\NLuvellia-senpai will go to waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've committed yet another \Nheinous act of betrayal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better hurry back before \Nshe gets suspicious...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OF COURSE SHE'S HERE, TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For today, let's start off \Nwith something quick and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my rest day...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rest day is the perfect time to get\Na jump on those other guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rest day is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others won't interrupt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*Note: The "right to veto" possessed by Peter\NGrill is assumed to be largely non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you and this Elf have grown quite\Nclose with each other lately, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate has a twisted sense of humor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow convinced her to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GODDAMMIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a total disaster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NONE of them have any intention \Nof following the rules...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are far too concerned \Nwith the pursuit of strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settling for second best isn't the\Nright attitude for a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I've had too much wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a wonderful time today, Peter-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for letting them ruin our date...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the world's strongest warrior,\Nyour popularity is only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I must bid you good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father tends to make a fuss \Nwhen I return home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Guildmaster can be... \Nkind of a worrywart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind going on a trip together\Noutside of our Guild duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere calm and relaxing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That sounds nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I... stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting her leave with this \Nawkwardness between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Peter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nut butter...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something doesn't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how much longer I'll be\Nable to endure their torture
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:11:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and still manage to protect my\Nrelationship with Luvellia-senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started out as a simple crush
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, you were my \Nbiggest source of strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till death do us part, \Nlet's grow old together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sincerest wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long time, by my side for all eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beaten down by our daily struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or soaked by a storm of rage;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get drenched, I won't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the umbrella that shields you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so cold... I'm by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smile of yours puts my soul at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could search the whole world over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And find no one like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the sight of you fills my heart with joy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much it may hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pledge my life to protecting you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Sir Peter Grill,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a letter from \NLuvellia-san the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9: Peter Grill and \Nthe Treaty's Aftermath
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?